Package com.irurueta.navigation.indoor

Class RangingReading<S extends RadioSource>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.Reading<S>
      • com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.RangingReading<S>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - a RadioSource type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RangingReadingLocated
    public class RangingReading<S extends RadioSource>
extends Reading<S>
    Contains a ranging reading associated to a given radio source (e.g. WiFi access point or bluetooth beacon), indicating the distance to such source.
